                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10035" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2529</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">460 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小小茯茶凭什么？解锁茯茶镇集团产业融合发展密码</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does Fu tea do it? Decoding Fu tea Town Group&#39;s industry integration.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨骏，赵宇娇，宋娟如，芦以晴，李婧雯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长安大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">夏明学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西咸新区茯茶镇文化产业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业融合；乡村振兴；文化传承；企业社会责任；国际化发展；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">industry integration; rural revitalization; cultural inheritance; corporate social responsibility; international development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦茯茶镇集团的产业融合创新实践，揭示其如何以“小小茶叶”为支点撬动多产业协同发展的大格局。作为扎根陕西泾阳的国有战略投资型企业，集团依托茯茶文化底蕴与“金花菌”核心优势，通过“产业融合”战略，将传统制茶工艺与现代科技、文化体验深度融合，构建覆盖种植加工、文创研发、数字商贸的多维产业体系。从“茶旅融合”激活乡村资源，到“以旅促商”打造特色商业街区和夜间经济新场景，再到“以茶养生”开发康养旅游项目，集团通过产业交叉协同拓展价值链，带动双赵村从“空心村”蜕变为宜居宜业的示范村。在经济效益之外，集团以数字化管理强化产业链协同，借力“村镇融合”模式盘活乡村资产，并搭乘“一带一路”快车推动茯茶品牌国际化，实现文化输出与产业升级的双重突破。案例旨在为传统产业转型升级、文化经济共生及城乡协同发展提供实践范本，展现企业社会责任与商业创新的深度融合。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the industrial integration and innovation practice of Fu tea Town Group, revealing how it leverages the overall pattern of multi-industry coordinated development with &quot;small tea&quot; as the fulcrum. As a state-owned strategic investment enterprise rooted in Jingyang, Shaanxi Province, the group relies on the cultural heritage of Fu tea and the core advantages of &quot;golden flower fungus&quot;, and deeply integrates traditional tea-making technology with modern science and technology, cultural tourism experience through the strategy of &quot;industrial integration&quot;, and builds a multi-dimensional industrial system covering planting and processing, cultural and creative research and development, and digital commerce. From the &quot;integration of tea and tourism&quot; to activate rural resources, to the creation of characteristic commercial blocks and new scenes of the night economy with &quot;tourism promotion&quot;, to the development of health tourism projects with &quot;tea health&quot;, the group has expanded the value chain through industrial cross-collaboration and driven Shuangzhao Village to transform from a &quot;hollow village&quot; to a livable and workable demonstration village. In addition to economic benefits, the Group strengthens the coordination of the industrial chain with digital management, revitalizes rural assets with the help of the &quot;village-town integration&quot; model, and takes the &quot;Belt and Road&quot; express to promote the internationalization of the Fu tea brand, achieving a double breakthrough in cultural output and industrial upgrading. The case aims to provide a practical model for the transformation and upgrading of traditional industries, cultural and economic symbiosis, and the coordinated development of urban and rural areas, demonstrating the deep integration of corporate social responsibility and business innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">VRIN理论；国有企业战略特性；产业融合理论；国际化产业融合以及战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
